Newest smartphones are shipping with massive advances in Sensor Technology and Geospatial Mapping capabilities.\u2028This is a major market shift happening away from stand-alone AR/VR apps to apps with AR/VR functionality embedded.
Integrating AR/VR into more popular social, mapping, ecommerce apps will make AR/VR available to the masses.
Brands and retailers are responding  and  ad revenue is trending  to overtaking paid AR/VR  app revenue in 2018.
